name: Mimi and Lala
description:
Mimi and Lala are twin puppies who live in the lavender fields, they love chocolate and red fruit ice cream, they love to walk and go picking flowers, paint rocks and sometimes dress up (usually Lala puts on wings to play that she is a fairy). They are totally inseparable and very happy 🐶🌈🐶🍦🧚

💖This is a super special piece for A4Astro's "Pairs and Mirrors" gallery 💖
